🔖 #100DaysOfCode Day 14:

I still get confused whenever I see a:
output <- data.table(aggregate(field1 ~ field2 + field3, input, FUN))

So I tried it with:
output <- input %>% 
group_by(field2, field3) %>% 
summarise(FUN=FUN(field1))

& yay it was /kind of/ the same 😅 #RStats
